### Disciplinary Actions API Testing

#### POST /api/disciplinary - Add Disciplinary Action
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/disciplinary \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "employeeName": "John Doe",
    "amount": 200.00,
    "reason": "Late submission",
    "date": "2026-03-01"
  }'
```

#### GET /api/disciplinary/{employeeName} - Get Employee Disciplinary Actions
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/disciplinary/John%20Doe
```

#### Payroll Integration Test
After adding disciplinary actions, the payroll calculation will automatically include them in the penalties field when calling:
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/payroll/John%20Doe?year=2026&month=3
```

The response will show the updated penalties field including disciplinary actions.
